==參選==
2020年，巴伊拉莫維奇受政黨{{le|波斯尼亞和黑塞哥維那美好未來聯盟|Union for a Better Future of BiH}}提名參選[[圖茲拉|圖茲拉]]市議員<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-09-14|title=SBB Tuzla: Sadašnji vijećnici predvode listu kandidata za GV Tuzla|trans-title=SBB Tuzla: The current councilors are leading the list of candidates for GV Tuzla|url=https://tuzlainfo.ba/index.php/novosti/item/24687-sbb-tuzla-sadasnji-vijecnici-predvode-listu-kandidata-za-gv-tuzla|access-date=2021-03-13|website=tuzlainfo.ba|language=hr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313143756/https://tuzlainfo.ba/index.php/novosti/item/24687-sbb-tuzla-sadasnji-vijecnici-predvode-listu-kandidata-za-gv-tuzla|archive-date=2021-03-13}}</ref>，但未能當選，當屆全國參選的20名羅姆女性無人當選，相較之下參選的47名羅姆男性有6人當選，巴伊拉莫維奇認為原因包括女性僅投身社區工作而不擅宣傳，以及許多新政黨參選造成選票分散，她希望日後羅姆人能在各選區推出一人參選以集中選票，但仍對此次參選的羅姆人較往屆為多表示肯定<ref name="UDAR2020">{{Cite news |last=Redakcija |date=2020-11-26 |title=IZBORI 2020: Romkinje nisu imale ravnopravan pristup medijima ni predstavljanju tokom kampanje |language=bs |trans-title=ELECTIONS 2020: Roma women did not have equal access to the media or representation during the campaign |work=Portal Udar |publisher=Elabsarajevo |location=Sarajevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina |url=https://www.portal-udar.net/izbori-2020-romkinje-nisu-imale-ravnopravan-pristup-medijima-ni-predstavljanju-tokom-kampanje/  |access-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313142434/https://www.portal-udar.net/izbori-2020-romkinje-nisu-imale-ravnopravan-pristup-medijima-ni-predstavljanju-tokom-kampanje/ |archive-date=March 13, 2021}}</ref>。

==獲獎==
2019年，巴伊拉莫維奇獲[[歐盟|歐盟]]頒發的歐盟羅姆融合獎（EU Award for Roma Integration）<ref name=eu>{{cite web|url=https://ec.europa.eu/neighbourhood-enlargement/sites/near/files/eu_award_for_roma_integration_2019_projects.pdf|title=EU Award for Roma Integration in the Western Balkans and Turkey|publisher=European Union|year=2019|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616050358/https://ec.europa.eu/neighbourhood-enlargement/sites/near/files/eu_award_for_roma_integration_2019_projects.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

